transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Hi, thank you for calling Viagra Escort Blue.

Speaker 2: How can I help you today?

Speaker 1: Sir, I put in to cancel and I still been—

Speaker 2: It's being charged.

Speaker 1: Okay, sir, let me pull up your account.

Speaker 2: Let's see what's going on, okay?

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: Can I get your full name and date of birth?

Speaker 1: Leroy Crenshaw, 7-11-1955.

Speaker 2: So, Leroy, the last order I have right here was from December and that was for the 50—

Speaker 1: Milligram Viagra, quantity of eight.

Speaker 2: Does that sound accurate?

Speaker 1: That's accurate, but I've been, you can try to, I canceled it in the beginning of—

Speaker 2: January.

Speaker 1: Okay, so I don't have anything on notes here.

Speaker 2: Did you give us a call to cancel it?

Speaker 1: No, I emailed you.

Speaker 2: Okay, so normally when you send an email, it will respond with an automatic email saying—

Speaker 1: That due to HIPAA rules that you have to call to confirm identity in order to make adjustments.

Speaker 2: Okay, so I don't see anything charged yet.

Speaker 1: It looks like your credit card company flagged it, right?

Speaker 2: Yes.

Speaker 1: So nothing has been charged yet.

Speaker 2: So that's good news to begin with.

Speaker 1: Now I want to talk about your prescription as a whole.

Speaker 2: Right now, you have a prescription dating back to 2022.

Speaker 1: There's some benefits to that.

Speaker 2: What that means is you are a VIP member here at ScoreBlue.

Speaker 1: You get a few perks with that per se.

Speaker 2: So right now, your perks right now is, meaning you have, this prescription is adjustable.

Speaker 1: You're not required to get it monthly how you have for the last three years.

Speaker 2: What we could do is put this on an extended pause, and that would allow you to call in—

Speaker 1: And place orders as needed in the future.

Speaker 2: So you don't need to get these every month.

Speaker 1: If, say, you want to refill three months from now, four months from now, you could give—

Speaker 2: Us a call, and then we could put that order through for you.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: I didn't know that.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: Yeah.

Speaker 1: What are the other perks?

Speaker 2: The other perks are, if you wanted, I could adjust your prescription to 100 milligrams—

Speaker 1: For the same cost.

Speaker 2: Well, see, and that's the problem that's going on.

Speaker 1: You, there's so much advertising out there that says you can get it for 98, 97 cents—

Speaker 2: Each, and I'm paying over $90 for one.

Speaker 1: Well, we, I don't think that's us.

Speaker 2: We don't have any pills that are 97 cents each.

Speaker 1: Now, a better, a price that I could get you is I could do 10 hundred milligrams for 63.95.

Speaker 2: I need less than that.

Speaker 1: I can't do less than that.

Speaker 2: That is the best deal on the market right now for the Viagra AGV.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: Then, put me on, I like that first option you had.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: So, you want me to put it on a pause for you?

Speaker 1: Yes.

Speaker 2: Put it on pause for six months.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: Yeah, and then you want me to adjust any future orders here?

Speaker 1: I can get you a better price for sure, I think.

Speaker 2: What kind of better price you going to give me?

Speaker 1: So, right now, you're paying for eight pills, 50 milligrams at 94.95.

Speaker 2: I can do 10 pills, 100 milligrams at $63.95.

Speaker 1: Well, not right now.

Speaker 2: I'm going to go with the pause.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: Well, I'm saying I can do both for you, Leroy, so I can pause it and then make sure your—

Speaker 1: Next order, you know, next time you call in is cheaper.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: Let's do that.

Speaker 2: Yes.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: I like that.

Speaker 1: Yeah.

Speaker 2: You don't need to order today.

Speaker 1: I just want to, you know, make sure we build the best program for you.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: Well, I like that 100 milligram.

Speaker 2: I can break them in half.

Speaker 1: Exactly.

Speaker 2: Exactly.

Speaker 1: All right, Leroy.

Speaker 2: I went ahead and made those adjustments.

Speaker 1: If you want to give us a call next time you place an order, they know here that they—

Speaker 2: Should be putting forth 100 milligrams, okay?

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: At what price?

Speaker 1: Correct.

Speaker 2: $63.95.

Speaker 1: So you're going to be saving about 30 bucks.

Speaker 2: Yes.

Speaker 1: Yes.

Speaker 2: That's a big saving.

Speaker 1: I need it.

Speaker 2: And two extra pills, too.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: All right.

Speaker 1: I'm going to make a note of that.

Speaker 2: So you got me down for the next to be on hold for six months, right?

Speaker 1: Yes, sir.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: That sounds good.

Speaker 2: All right.

Speaker 1: Yeah, you're all set, Leroy.

Speaker 2: You're good to go.

Speaker 1: Outstanding.

Speaker 2: Thank you, sir.

Speaker 1: You're very welcome.

Speaker 2: Happy to help.

Speaker 1: All right.

Speaker 2: Thank you.

Speaker 1: Bye-bye.

Speaker 2: Bye-bye.
